<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Indexoutofrangeexception on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/indexoutofrangeexception/</link><description>Recent content in Indexoutofrangeexception on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/indexoutofrangeexception/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>IndexOutOfRangeException</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fsharp/index-out-of-range/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fsharp/index-out-of-range/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An &lt;code&gt;IndexOutOfRangeException&lt;/code&gt; is thrown when you try to access an element of an array or collection using an index that is less than zero or greater than or equal to the collection&amp;rsquo;s length.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Off-by-one errors in loops&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Using negative indices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accessing array beyond its length&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Incorrect index calculation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fsharp" data-lang="fsharp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Accessing beyond array bounds
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; arr &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[|&lt;/span&gt;1&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; 2&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; 3&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; x &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; arr&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.[&lt;/span&gt;3&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// IndexOutOfRangeException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Use valid index
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; arr &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[|&lt;/span&gt;1&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; 2&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; 3&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; x &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; arr&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.[&lt;/span&gt;2&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// 3 (zero-indexed)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fsharp" data-lang="fsharp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: No bounds check
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; getElement idx &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;arr&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;a array&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; arr&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.[&lt;/span&gt;idx&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Check bounds first
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; getElement idx &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;arr&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;a array&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; idx &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;=&lt;/span&gt; 0 &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; idx &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; arr&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;Length &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;then&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; Some arr&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.[&lt;/span&gt;idx&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; None
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fsharp" data-lang="fsharp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: Off by one
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; arr &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[|&lt;/span&gt;10&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; 20&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; 30&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;arr&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.[&lt;/span&gt;arr&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;Length&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// IndexOutOfRangeException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: Negative index
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; list &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;1&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; 2&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; 3&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;list&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.[-&lt;/span&gt;1&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// IndexOutOfRangeException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 3: Empty collection
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; empty &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; Array.empty&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;int&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;empty&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.[&lt;/span&gt;0&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// IndexOutOfRangeException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fsharp/argument-exception"&gt;ArgumentException&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fsharp/null-reference5"&gt;NullReferenceException&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>